{"tid":2330900,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"香港電台：悉尼北部海灘區增至28人確診　病毒株或源自美國","createTime":"2020-12-18T10:57:50.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-18T15:38:28.000Z","uid":290404,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"707404a97a89e5011eb7a2e884902c500a3886e2","tid":2330900,"uid":290404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-18T10:57:50.000Z","msg":"澳洲悉尼北部海灘地區再多10人確診新型肺炎，令當地的感染個案增至28宗。<br />\n<br />\n悉尼過去兩星期都沒新增的本土病例，北部海灘地區的居民被要求留在家中，直至下星期一。新南威爾士州州長說，如果幾天內無法控制疫情，可能會實施更多限制措施，敦促民眾在公共場所要戴口罩，並保持高度戒備。<br />\n<br />\n有州政府官員說，測試顯示，<strong>悉尼北部海灘地區發現的病毒株，與在美國入境人士身上發現的病毒株一致，暫時未知病毒如何進入社區。</strong><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1565953-20201218.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1565953-20201218.htm&d=PGKZrCzpIeFm7bz4D1EKrb32HZRMtn4xjJY4gFhUisg%3D&h=40b2e23f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1565953-20201218.htm&h=a9bcd4dd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1565953-20201218.htm</a>"},{"pid":"d91067a0784eaf84087f392ef147368fd391eeb0","tid":2330900,"uid":53062,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-18T10:59:29.000Z","msg":"樓主不如叫港台狙擊手，日日貼港台新聞"},{"pid":"9b8d8e85826d051db34661516f9119ecb606f190","tid":2330900,"uid":290404,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"d91067a0784eaf84087f392ef147368fd391eeb0","tid":2330900,"uid":53062,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-18T10:59:29.000Z","msg":"樓主不如叫港台狙擊手，日日貼港台新聞"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-18T11:01:03.000Z","msg":"睇開港台新聞啊嗎<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"356727556e95bc468d9cfe73af4b3ea119da3aca","tid":2330900,"uid":60366,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-18T11:15:26.000Z","msg":"有錢人區<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2890576968d98e6411a0831c295fa9f97d341fc0","tid":2330900,"uid":240362,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"d91067a0784eaf84087f392ef147368fd391eeb0","tid":2330900,"uid":53062,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-18T10:59:29.000Z","msg":"樓主不如叫港台狙擊手，日日貼港台新聞"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-18T11:34:16.000Z","msg":"港台新聞唔需要亦唔應該係「黃」,一向以來是否秉持中立相信自有公論,而好似#1樓主咁刻意混淆視聽係需要譴責同指出<br />\n<br />\n句野係衛生首長Kerry Chant講,樓主刻意將標題改到好似港台説法,同內文迴避&quot;有州政府官員說&quot;,實在居心叵測<br />\n<br />\n&quot;Chief Health Officer Kerry Chant said genomic testing suggested the strain circulating on the Northern Beaches was from the US.<br />\n<br />\nDr Chant said there was some similarity between the Northern Beaches strain and a strain found in an overseas traveller who was in hotel quarantine.&quot;"},{"pid":"10efa699060f6dd53a42edf257de2bf15882637d","tid":2330900,"uid":17103,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-18T11:47:01.000Z","msg":"was some similarity<br />\n一致<br />\n<br />\n又學到新英文"},{"pid":"990d5e7febbb0f8b94554d0af07e369645a890ea","tid":2330900,"uid":199771,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-18T11:49:59.000Z","msg":"美國病毒"},{"pid":"7ada4b617401b8d163ebea3ec19c3c3c5ee2e043","tid":2330900,"uid":70786,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"10efa699060f6dd53a42edf257de2bf15882637d","tid":2330900,"uid":17103,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-18T11:47:01.000Z","msg":"was some similarity<br />\n一致<br />\n<br />\n又學到新英文"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-18T11:50:34.000Z","msg":"翻譯唔使講信達雅<br />\n講忠誠就可以<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2629e01874b7d0d5b563fed24c59f861dc36b95e","tid":2330900,"uid":378294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"990d5e7febbb0f8b94554d0af07e369645a890ea","tid":2330900,"uid":199771,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"